{"tid":1568690,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"關於保護暴力藍絲的\"左膠\"處理方法","createTime":"2019-09-14T10:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T12:44:41.000Z","uid":189803,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"72b00cc74a4ff0121c7c6b62c4517ae933f0df5c","tid":1568690,"uid":189803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"我有時都覺得幾搞笑, 點解保護打鳩手足的藍絲就係&quot;左膠&quot;<br />\n似乎定義左佢係反送中的一員, 都係示威者, 係做法唔同咁<br />\n但事實上係無直接証據佢係示威者<br />\n立場條片條友直接認佢係暴力藍絲大佬, 所以保佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/434270730521162/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F434270730521162%2F&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=b9f6ddf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/434270730521162/</a><br />\n所以, 以後所有保暴力藍絲的人, 同暴力藍絲係一鳩樣, 唔好再用左膠定義佢地<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地唔係無辜</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2d10f6bab3d75711eb63cf491b9224021ae37f7c","tid":1568690,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72a01d23efc81754d328df174bafe4716d5710b0","tid":1568690,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca9fd299fa982e78069d1c0f49f766bedde75a48","tid":1568690,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:58:17.000Z","msg":"連儂牆 AIRDROP<br />\n<br />\n915 915 915 915 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"